<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu thisan leh A dikna,
 Lo kinepna dang ka nei puoi;
 A hawihpen le ka ging ngam puoi,
 Isu min mai ah ka kingai.

[V2]
 Krista Suong tikhat ah ka ding,
 Mun dang cheng chuh pilnel ahi. (2)

[V3]
 2. Thimnan A mel hawih a lieh tieng,
 A lungsiet danglo ah chawl ka;
 Guohpi, huihpi hat nuoi ale,
 Mun muongah thikdet in ei tui.

[V4]
 3. A tiem, A thuthun, A thisan,
 Tuilien lakah kei ei panpih;
 Ka thagau a lungkham laiin,
 Ka kinep leh umna ahi.

[V5]
 4. Pengkun gi tawh A hung tieng leh,
 Ziechun Ama-ah um ing-ka;
 A dikna maia kithuom in,
 A ma-ah dembei a ding di'n.</lyrics>
<title>THE SOLID ROCK</title>
<hymn_number>205</hymn_number>
</song>